      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and<strong> ginger</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 2 min</p><p>Add the <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ground paprika</strong>, <strong>ground coriander</strong> and <strong>ground cumin</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
